# HST Client Walkthrough (Updated)

Tai lieu nay mo ta luong chay that cua frontend Nuxt theo code hien tai.
Muc tieu: nguoi moi vao project doc xong co the hieu cach route, fetch data, va mo rong trang moi ma khong doan.

## 1) Kien truc tong quan

- Frontend: Nuxt (SSR + CSR).
- Backend: Laravel API (hien tai chu yeu co `common/header` va `pages/home/*`).
- FE khong goi Laravel truc tiep tu component. FE goi qua Nitro server API trong `server/api/*`.

Luong tong quat:

1. Request vao Nuxt route.
2. Layout load global data (header) qua store.
3. Page load du lieu rieng.
4. SSR render HTML.
5. Client hydrate va dieu huong tiep theo theo SPA.

## 2) Routing hien tai

### 2.1 Trang tinh

- `app/pages/index.vue`: Trang chu.
- `app/pages/website-demos/index.vue`
- `app/pages/website-demo/index.vue`

### 2.2 Dynamic route catch-all

- `app/pages/[...slug].vue`

File nay la router dong cho cac URL khac route tinh.
No khong dung `/api/pages/resolve` nua.
Thay vao do, no resolve theo menu tu Laravel:

1. Fetch `common/header`.
2. Flatten `main_menu.items` + children.
3. Match URL hien tai voi `item.url`.
4. Neu khong match -> 404.

Guard 404 som cho system prefix:

- `/api`
- `/admin`
- `/storage`
- `/_nuxt`
- `/__nuxt`
- `/build`
- `/vendor`

## 3) Cach dynamic page duoc map

Trong `app/pages/[...slug].vue`, thu tu map component:

1. Map theo `css_class`:
   - `page-contact` -> `ContactPage`
   - `contact` -> `ContactPage`
2. Map theo `reference_id`:
   - `13` -> `app/pages/website-demo/index.vue`
   - `21` -> `app/pages/website-demos/index.vue`
3. Map theo alias URL:
   - `/contact`
   - `/lien-he`
   - `/lien-he-voi-chung-toi`
   -> `ContactPage`
4. Neu khong roi vao case nao -> `MenuFallbackPage`.

Component lien quan:

- `app/components/pages/contact-page.vue`
- `app/components/pages/menu-fallback.vue`

## 4) Vi sao co luc thay loading bar, co luc khong

Global loading bar nam o:

- `app/app.vue` (`<NuxtLoadingIndicator .../>`)

No chi hien khi dieu huong co do tre du de thay.
Neu route resolve rat nhanh (vi data da cache), bar co the khong kip hien.

Vi du:

- Click contact: thuong nhanh do `headerData` da cache trong store.
- Click home: thuong co them request section/meta nen de thay loading hon.

## 5) Global data (Header) va cache

Store:

- `app/stores/common.ts`

Ham `fetchHeader(locale)` co cache logic:

- Neu da co `headerData` cung locale -> return ngay, khong goi API lai.

Composable:

- `app/composables/common/useHeader.ts`

Su dung `useAsyncData` de SSR doi co header truoc khi render.
Khi doi locale, store reset va fetch lai.

## 6) Page store dung de resolve route theo menu

File:

- `app/stores/page.ts`

`resolvePage(slug, locale)` hien tai:

1. Fetch header trong common store.
2. Flatten menu.
3. Tim item co `item.url` trung voi `slug`.
4. Gan vao `currentPage`.

Store nay da bo logic goi `/api/pages/resolve`.

## 7) Server API bridge (Nuxt -> Laravel)

### 7.1 Header

- `server/api/common/header.get.ts`
- Forward toi Laravel: `/common/header`

### 7.2 Home page APIs

- `server/api/pages/home/meta.get.ts` -> `/pages/home/meta`
- `server/api/pages/home/section/[section].get.ts` -> `/pages/home/section/{section}`

### 7.3 Generic slug APIs (Nuxt co, backend co the chua co)

- `server/api/pages/[slug]/meta.get.ts` -> `/pages/{slug}/meta`
- `server/api/pages/[slug]/section/[section].get.ts` -> `/pages/{slug}/section/{section}`

Luu y:

- Theo backend Laravel hien tai (`admin/routes/api.php`), route dong `{slug}` chua duoc expose.
- Vi vay cac endpoint dang `/pages/{slug}/...` co the 404 voi slug khac `home`.
- Dynamic route FE hien tai giai quyet bang menu mapping (khong phu thuoc `pages/resolve`).

## 8) Them 1 dynamic page moi (khong doi backend)

Quy trinh de an toan:

1. Tao component page moi trong `app/components/pages/`, vi du `about-page.vue`.
2. Mo `app/pages/[...slug].vue`.
3. Them map:
   - Uu tien map theo `css_class` (on dinh nhat): vi du `page-about`.
   - Neu can, map them theo `reference_id`.
   - Neu can nua, them alias URL.
4. Test dieu huong tu menu.
5. Neu khong map thi route se roi vao `MenuFallbackPage`.

Khuyen nghi:

- Uu tien map bang `css_class` trong Laravel admin de khong phu thuoc slug.
- Chi dung alias URL cho truong hop tam thoi.

## 9) Quy uoc coding

1. Goi section data qua composable:
   - `usePageSection('home', 'section-name')`
2. Trong server API, dung `apiFetch` + `getLocale(event)`.
3. Khi doc response section, unwrap an toan:
   - `raw?.data || raw || null`
4. Data dung chung giua nhieu page dat trong Pinia store.
5. Khong tai tao logic resolve slug o tung component; tap trung o `[...slug].vue`.

## 10) Tinh trang hien tai can nho

- `pages/resolve` khong ton tai tren backend.
- Dynamic slug hien tai la menu-driven routing.
- Contact page da duoc them de lam mau cho dynamic page.
